    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把两个参与者加进去了。现在图上有Client和Server两条生命线，基础框架搭好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
